{"tid":2195014,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下有咩可以取代小米手環？","createTime":"2020-09-09T01:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:23:22.000Z","uid":242602,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3c04d54967739bb6c295b5f128b7f5612ab28b","tid":2195014,"uid":242602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"小弟個老母本身有隻小米手環，但係佢開始藍轉黃，想脫離大陸嘅牌子<br />\n<br />\n咁啱佢隻手環壞咗，想換過個，問我買咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係要幾點：<br />\n- 電池夠耐，唔好好似有Mon表咁幾日差一次，最好好似小米咁幾個禮拜一次<br />\n- 可以show 電話 notification （老母工作需要）<br />\n- log行路步數<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴打有咩推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />價錢可以貴過小米，無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e0c877642597db9e78edbdf0e5102c8488f30c","tid":2195014,"uid":219537,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:32:36.000Z","msg":"華為手環"},{"pid":"58844636de7e7958fc3ff99d560c239eaded0739","tid":2195014,"uid":277599,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:34:33.000Z","msg":"繼續用返小米算啦"},{"pid":"c3b9f62ed9d078d0c9c64672866b2f258874de06","tid":2195014,"uid":277599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"or fitbit唔錯"},{"pid":"6b81e5b83126cd89021a5b4cbc5261e176ae308b","tid":2195014,"uid":222581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85b3bede49c64a44eb4cff6c96c71a9c7b2ceeba","tid":2195014,"uid":285361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"samsung fit"},{"pid":"42deba62d7e2a2515fa6752129b624dde4474881","tid":2195014,"uid":10162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"apple watch"},{"pid":"53fe8b8d56e2773bb0f09c69a37855db072c21a8","tid":2195014,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09